  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un mi/ ja tu manna poijſcht/ raobix ir wiſch wiſſi\nPreekſchâ ſtaigaji/ ittin ka taws ſcho Launu pahr teim weddiſ.\nTehws Dahwids irr ſtaigajs/\nun darrift pehz wiſſu/ ko es tew\netimu pawehſeis/ un turreſi man-\nnus Likkumns un mannu Teeſu."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad apſtiprinaſchu es ta-\nwu Walſtibas Krehtlu/ ittin ka\nes weenu Derribu darrijs ar ta-\nwn Tehwu Dahwidu / tazzi-\ndams: Tew ne trvhks ne kahds\nWilrs/ kas pahr Iſraelu wal-\ndihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja juhs atkahpfeetees/\nun atſahfceet mannuš Likkumus/\nun mannuš Banſlus/ ko es jums\nefinu dewis/ un eejeet/ un kalpo-\nfeet ſweſcheem Deeweem/ un pa-\nflannifeetees preekſch teem."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad iſfaknoſchu es tohs\nno mannas Semmes Wirſus/\nko es teem eſinu dewis/ un at-\nmettiſchu ſcho Nammu / ko es\nmannam Wahrdam eſinu ſweh-\ntijs/ un darrifchu to par takka-\nmu Wahrdu un Paſakku ſtarp\nwiſſahm Tantahm."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr ſcho Namminu /\nkas tik angsts bijts/ buhs wiſ-\nfam/ kas fezzen eet/ iſtruhzina-\ntees/ un ſazziht: Kapehz irr tas\nKUNGS ſchat Semmei un\nſchim Namman ta un ta darrijs?"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tapē ſazzihts: Ta-\npehz ka tee to KUNGU ſawo\nTehwo Deewu irr atſahjuſchi/\nkas tohs no Egiptes- Semmes\nirr iſweddis/ un irr pee zitteem\nDeeweem turreiſchees/un preekſch\nteem flanniiſchees/ un teemi kal."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta VIII. Nodalla.\nSalamans uſtaisa rahbus Pilsfahtus:\nſpeesch tohs atliſkuſchus Paganus pee Meſ-\nlu Dohſchanas : 7. Salamana Augſtinceſ-\ndimi ſints un peeſdefsnits Pulkâ : 10. Tah-\nDeetwa Kalpoſchanas Eezelfchana : 12. Sa-\nlamans leek ar leeſahm Laiwahmi eet us Do-\nwiru/Seltuatnet : 17."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wn pehz diwiſeſmitis\nGaddeem / kad Sala-\nmans ta KUNGA\nNammu un farvu Nammu bij\ndarrijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad uſtaisija Salamans\ntohs Pilsfahtus/ ko Urains Sa-\nlamanam bij dewis / nn likke\ntohs Iſraëta Behrnus tur dſih-\nwoht."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz zehlahs Salamans\nus Eemat Zowu / un apſtipri-\nnaja to."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſsch uſtaisija arridsan\nTadmorn Inkſneti/ un wiſſus\nSpikkeru Pilsfahtus/ ko wiſsch\nEemata darrija."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſsch uſtaisija arridsan\nto Kalna- un leijas Bet-Ohronu/\nſtiprus Pilsfahtus ar Muhreem/\nWahrtim un Preekſchſchauja-\nmein."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir Baēlatu / un wiſſus\nSpikkeru Pilsfahtus/ kas Sa-\nlamanam peederreja/ ir wiſſus\nRattu un Jahtneeku Pilsfah-\ntus un wiſſ/ kas Salamanam\ngribbejahs taiſiht Jeruſaleme un\nus Libbani/ un wiſſas winna\nSemmes Walſtis."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſus atliſkuſchus Lau-\nQoooo"
    }
  ],
